A Tale of Tenali Ramakrishna: -
______________________________________
The Witty Poet of Krishna Devaraya‚Äôs Court, Blessed by Goddess Kali, Tenali Rama earned the title "Vikatakavi" (The Witty Poet) for his sharp intellect. Despite personal struggles, he rose to become the esteemed Aasthana Kavi (Court Poet) of Emperor Krishna Devaraya. With clever solutions to complex problems, he won the kingdom‚Äôs admiration, leaving a lasting legacy as one of history‚Äôs most brilliant minds.

snippet.title: Projapati Song | Projapati 2 | Mithun C | Dev | Jeet Gannguli | Avijit Senn | ‚Ä™Bengal Talkies
snippet.description:
Presenting the official video of the ‚ÄúProjpati ‚Äù title track from the much-awaited film Projapati 2.
‚ÄúProjapati Song‚Äù is a high-octane Bengali wedding dance anthem packed with celebration, colour, and unstoppable energy. Composed in a Jeet-Ganguly‚Äìstyle festive dance beat.

The lyrics carry the fun, poetic, and rhythmic flavour you‚Äôd expect from a Priyo-Chattopadhyay‚Äìinspired wedding track‚Äîfull of joy, jokes, and pure celebration. Featuring the dynamic screen presence of Dev‚Äôs youthful energy and Mithun Chakraborty‚Äôs iconic swag, the track feels like a grand family celebration turned into a dance explosion.

snippet.description:
Presenting ‚ÄúPheriasa Tume Humane‚Äù a heartfelt musical tribute to our Odisha‚Äôs voice, legend and emotion, Late Humane Sagar.
This song is not just music it is a feeling, a memory and a goodbye to the man whose voice touched millions of hearts.

Sung soulfully by Swetalin Panda, and beautifully written & composed by Sujit Muduli, this tribute keeps alive the presence, voice and legacy of Odisha's most loved singer, Humane Sagar.

üíê Rest in Peace Humane Sagar ‚Äî You will live forever through your songs and voice. Odisha will never forget you.

snippet.description:
vidiyo 1
Madam Ji (Official Video) Masoom Sharma | Amar Karnawal, Pinna Music | New Haryanvi Song 2025 
  
#madamji #masoomsharma #amarkarnawal #pinnamusic #newharyanvisong2025 #newharyanvisongs2025 #haryanvisongs2025 #haryanvisongs #haryanvisong 

Title : Madam Ji
Singer / Composer - Masoom Sharma 
Female Singer - Rekha Goswami
Music - Pinna Music
Lyrics - Amar Karnawal
Project By : Vikas Rajana

Label : @masoomsharma

SUBSCRIBE :    / @masoomsharma  

Contact For More Information
‚ñ∫ FACEBOOK :   / iammasoomsharma  
‚ñ∫ INSTAGRAM : https://bit.ly/3g8Haln

Distribution Partner : Ziaan Entertainment FZCO

Lyrics :
Ho Tu Kyun Rakhta Hai Bin Baat Mein
Itna Asla Apne Sath Mein
Saiyan Tu To Superstar Tha
Ban Gaya Kya Tu Raaton Raat Mein
Hath Mein Asla Gaat Mein Jaan
Minute Mein Khada Khinda Dyan Saang
Karya Koi Maada Na Pareshan
Re Dushman Ke Banwadya Than
Baje 47 Ke Fire, Raat Ne Gunje Shehar
Je Hoja Mahra Kise Te Bair
Fer Ude Manas Marte Hain
Re Hum To Gunde Hain Madam Ji, Gundagardi Karte Hain
Vahan Tera Shehar Thehar Jata Hai Jahan Se Hum Guzarte Hain

Ho Raakhe Tu Balam Gaadi Kaali
Diggi Mein Rakha 47
Bole Koye Tere Te Aadha
Uske Munh Pe Laade Taali
Mhari Dhaak Chale Se Thaddi
Raat Ne Piven Hath Ki Kaadi
Rakhu Automatic Asla
Madam Automatic Gaadi
 Baddi Soch Approach Sifarish
Ghar Ka Iklota Vaaris
Hoja Ek Phone Pe Baarish
Khulle Round Baraste Hain
Re Hum To Gunde Hain Madam Ji, Gundagardi Karte Hain
Vahan Tera Shehar Thehar Jata Hai Jahan Se Hum Guzarte Hain

Manne Tere Kaale Kaam Na Bhaate
Yaar Tere Bank Mein 15 Khaate
Rapiye Ginti Mein Aate
Log Ke Kare Samajh Ni Paate
Re Dhandhe Gorya Mein Karu Kale
Asle Rakhu Russia Aale
Sheikha Gelyan Gadhi Yaari
Paadu Baith Dubai Mein Chaale
Re Tera Karnawaliya Pakka Paapi
Amar Bas Eke Naam Se Kaafi
Darshan Honde Koni Baaki
Milan Ne Log Taraste Hain
Re Hum To Gunde Hain Madam Ji, Gundagardi Karte Hain
Vahan Tera Shehar Thehar Jata Hai Jahan Se Hum Guzarte Hain
